methods.contains:
Determines if the specified time is within the business period.

:param time: (io.deephaven.time.DateTime) - time.
:return: (boolean) true if the time is in this period; otherwise, false.
methods.getEndTime:
Returns the end of the period.

:return: (io.deephaven.time.DateTime) the end of the period
methods.getLength:
Returns the length of the period in nanoseconds.

:return: (long) length of the period in nanoseconds
methods.getStartTime:
Returns the start of the period.

:return: (io.deephaven.time.DateTime) the start of the period

text: A period of business time during a business day.
